### List all authors
GET http://localhost:3000/authors

### Get an author by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/authors/1

### Create an author
POST http://localhost:3000/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "any_name",
  "email": "any_email@example.com"
}

### Update an author
PUT http://localhost:3000/authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "updated_name",
  "email": "any_email@example.com"
}
